the most dangerous man in america : daniel &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and the pentagon papers is a 2009 documentary film directed by judith ehrlich and rick goldsmith . the film follows daniel &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and explores the events leading up to the publication of the pentagon papers , which exposed the top-secret military history of the united states involvement in vietnam . the film was shown on the pbs series pov in 2010 , for which it earned a peabody award .